DESCRIPTION:Families and individuals who need a quiet\, uncrowded environme
 nt are invited to use the library before we open. Explore the Kids Room\, 
 Teen Room\, Studio\, and materials on the first floor.Enjoy games\, crafts
 \, and the option to interact with Rainbow Animal Assisted Therapy dogs. A
 daptive supports and the Sensory Break Room will be available.Registration
