DESCRIPTION:This month we'll be discussing The Connellys of County Down by 
 Tracey Lange.After serving 18 months on a drug charge\, 30-year-old Tara C
 onnelly returns home to live with her siblings. As she works to build a ne
 w career and hold her family together\, especially when secrets threaten t
 o tear them apart forever\, she finds love in a most unlikely place.All ar
 e welcome\, whether you read in print\, braille\, audio\, or simply want t
 o join the conversation. Engage in whatever way feels comfortable for you.
 Request the book from the Talking Book & Braille Service.Find The Connelly
 s of County Down in the library catalog.Find titles by Tracey Lange in the
  library catalog.
