LAST-MODIFIED:20250921T040655Z
UID:10001170-1773862200-1773862200@northshorecenter.org
SUMMARY:North Shore Center Presents: Joanne Shaw Taylor
DESCRIPTION:Experience the magic of Joanne Shaw Taylor and her incredible band as they deliver a powerhouse performance featuring songs from her latest album\, Black & Gold. \nRenowned for her electrifying guitar performances and soulful songwriting\, Joanne’s vocals shine as she blends blues\, rock\, soul\, and pop. The show also includes standout tracks from earlier albums and heartfelt tributes to classic blues legends. As one of today’s most dynamic performers\, Joanne Shaw Taylor promises an unforgettable night of music.
URL:https://northshorecenter.org/event/joanne-shaw-taylor/
LOCATION:George Van Dusen Theatre
CATEGORIES:Music,North Shore Center Presents
END:VEVENT
