DESCRIPTION:A Beautiful Day in the NeighborhoodTom Hanks received an Oscar 
 nomination for playing Fred Rogers\, creator of the beloved TV show\, Mist
 er Rogers' Neighborhood. The story follows Lloyd Vogel\, a cynical reporte
 r assigned to write a profile on Fred Rogers for a magazine article about 
 heroes. He has a reputation for being hard on his subjects and holds much 
 anger toward life in general\, his father in particular. His interviews wi
 th Fred Rogers have a profound effect on his outlook and help him to learn
  how to forgive. Starring Starring Tom Hanks\, Matthew Rhys\, Susan Kelec
 hi Watson\, and Chris Cooper.2019 : 109 minutes : Rated PG for some strong
  thematic material\, a brief fight\, and some mild language: DramaFree tic
 kets will be given to those who attend.Watch a trailer for A Beautiful Day
  in the Neighborhood.Find A Beautiful Day in the Neighborhood in the libra
 ry catalog.
CATEGORIES:Movie,Women's History Month
