SUMMARY:Sunday Afternoon with HERstory: Trailblazing Female Firsts (R)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.lincolnwoodlibrary.org/event/sunday-afternoon-her
 story-trailblazing-female-firsts-r-33633
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260114T022800Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260116T004235Z
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Women’s History Month with Chicago cabaret artists 
 Catherine Thomson and Anita Kallen in HERstory: Trailblazing Female Firsts
 . Through songs by Harold Arlen\, Stephen Schwartz\, Dolly Parton\, Tom Le
 hrer\, Kander & Ebb\, Sara Bareilles\, and more\, they shine a spotlight o
 n the women who boldly defied expectations and changed history. Enjoy insp
 iring stories\, dynamic performances\, and a musical tribute to the trailb
 lazers who paved the way.
CATEGORIES:Movies\, Music & Entertainment
DTSTART:20260322T190000Z
DTEND:20260322T200000Z
LOCATION:4000 W. Pratt Ave.\, Lincolnwood\, IL\, 60712\, US
ROOM:Meeting Room A/B
GEO:42.0047721;-87.7292067
