X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Lincolnwood Library": "https://www.lincolnwoodlibrary.org/event/monday-matinees-33683"}
X-SOURCE-ID:lincolnwood_library
X-SOURCE:Lincolnwood Library
UID:33683
DTSTAMP:20260313T022002Z
SUMMARY:Monday Matinees
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.lincolnwoodlibrary.org/event/monday-matinees-3368
 3
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260115T152156Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260116T005321Z
DESCRIPTION:Enjoy great films at your library every Monday! Doors open at 1
 2:45pm.  Father of the Bride (1991)Mon\, Mar 2 • 1-2:45pm • PG\, 10
 0 mins •  [D]In this remake of the 1950 comedy\, a frazzled shoe execut
 ive tries to cope with the financial and emotional costs of his only daugh
 ter's impending marriage while also dealing with an eccentric wedding coor
 dinator. **Paulie (1998)Mon\, Mar 9 • 1-2:45pm • PG\, 91 mins •  
 [D]A chatty parrot named Paulie recalls his search to find the little girl
  who first owned him and gets help from a kind janitor. Wicked: For Good
  (2025)Mon\, Mar 23 • 1-3:30pm • PG\, 138 mins •  [D]Now demonized
  as the Wicked Witch of the West\, Elphaba lives in exile in the Ozian for
 est\, while Glinda resides at the palace in Emerald City\, reveling in the
  perks of fame and popularity. As an angry mob rises against the Wicked Wi
 tch\, she'll need to reunite with Glinda to transform herself\, and all of
  Oz\, for good. The Long Walk (2025)Mon\, Mar 30 • 1-3pm • R\, 108 m
 ins •  [D]In a dystopian near-future\, 100 teenage boys must embark on 
 an annual competitive test known as "The Long Walk." The rules are simple:
  maintain a speed above 4 miles per hour. Receive three warnings in an hou
 r and you're shot dead. The last one walking gets whatever he wants for th
 e rest of his life. Under these grim circumstances\, the boys develop deep
  friendships despite knowing that each of their friends' survival is a thr
 eat to their own. There will be no Monday Matinee on March 16 due to the 
 library serving as a polling location.
CATEGORIES:Movies\, Music & Entertainment
DTSTART:20260323T180000Z
DTEND:20260323T204500Z
LOCATION:4000 W. Pratt Ave.\, Lincolnwood\, IL\, 60712\, US
ROOM:Meeting Room A/B
GEO:42.0047721;-87.7292067
