SUMMARY:Online Apéro Conversation
DESCRIPTION:Alliance Française du North Shore\nMeet fellow Francophones for evening conversation. This gathering is facilitated by one or more of our native or fluent AFduNS leaders.\n\nPour yourself a glass of wine\, gather some snacks and settle in at home for our online conversation group.\n\nThe meeting will be held on Zoom. Although you don't need to download Zoom to attend this meeting\, we encourage you to do so (https://zoom.us/download) for a smoother experience. Depending on the number of attendees\, we may break out into smaller groups.\n\nThe link to the meeting will be visible when you RSVP. The meeting ID is 859 8255 4800.\n\nAll fluency levels are welcome. RSVPs help us plan.\n\n**Membership in the AFduNS**\nWhile no membership is required for newcomers\, we welcome new members whose membership will support the activities of the AFduNS\, a nonprofit 501(c)(3) organization. For further info\, visit our [website](https://afnorthshore.org/events) or [click here to contact us](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScRxM03DpryO_lZlGWK-aDOCiFHFbivJimTScMOQmWk7KgOJQ/viewform?pli=1). If you wish to join the AFduNS\, you may sign up [online](https://afnorthshore.org/join). Annual dues are $50.00.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/afnorthshore/events/313077527/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260127T093527Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260127T093527Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/5/a/4/4/600_480743108.jpeg
END:VEVENT
