DESCRIPTION:Alliance Française du North Shore\nCan't make it to the daytime café conversations? Then join us for coffee and/or wine at [Oak at The Glen](https://www.oakattheglen.com/). Appetizers are also available.\n\nAll fluency levels are welcome.\n\nFor further information\, visit www.AFnorthshore.org.\n\n**Membership in the AFduNS**\n\nWhile no membership is required for newcomers\, we welcome new members whose membership will support the activities of the AFduNS\, a nonprofit 501(c)(3) organization. For further info\, visit our [website](https://afnorthshore.org/events) or [click here to contact us](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScRxM03DpryO_lZlGWK-aDOCiFHFbivJimTScMOQmWk7KgOJQ/viewform?pli=1). If you wish to join the AFduNS\, you may sign up [online](https://afnorthshore.org/join). Annual dues are $50.00.
