 ore gift card\, a bento box\, and a meal prep cookbook!\n\n \n\nThe first 5
 0 participants will receive a complimentary mason jar with a healthy breakf
 ast recipe attached.\n\n \n\nHealthy snacks will also be provided during th
 e event. If you are unable to attend in person\, please register to attend 
 virtually.\n\n \n\nAll students\, faculty\, and staff are welcome!
