LAST-MODIFIED:20260119T145554Z
DESCRIPTION:Join presenter Carolyn Armenta Davis for Feminine Footprints\, 
 a powerful look at ten groundbreaking African American women whose achieve
 ments helped shape history. Drawn from her award-winning 1978 network radi
 o series profiling 65 Black women trailblazers\, this program highlights t
 he courage\, creativity\, and lasting impact of these inspiring pioneers.
