DESCRIPTION:SmurfsIn this computer-animated musical comedy reboot of The Sm
 urfs movie series\, the wizard Gargamel and his power-hungry brother Razam
 el are up to no good. They kidnap Papa Smurf\, who is hiding a living/talk
 ing magical book named Jaunty. If the brothers can control Jaunty\, they'l
 l be one step closer to total evil dominance. Smurfette (voiced by Rihanna
 ) and other Smurfs\, including No Name Smurf and Papa Smurf's estranged br
 other Ken\, partner with unlikely allies on an action-packed rescue missio
 n that takes them from their world to the human world to stop the wizardly
  villainy. File this under blue fun.Featuring the voice talents of Rihanna
 \, James Corden\, Nick Offerman\, Jp Karliak\, Daniel Levy\, Amy Sedaris\,
  Natasha Lyonne\, Sandra Oh\, Jimmy Kimmel\, Octavia Spencer\, Nick Kroll\
 , Hannah Waddingham\, Alex Winter\, Maya Erskine\, Kurt Russell\, and John
  Goodman.Free tickets will be given to all who attend. 2025 : 90 minutes 
 : PG for action\, language and some rude humor : Animated comedyWatch the 
 trailer for Smurfs.Find Smurfs in the library catalog.
CATEGORIES:Movie
