STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251201T223443Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251229T192144Z
DESCRIPTION:Chicago plays the blues a little bit differently. When the blue
 s performers came from the Mississippi Delta to the packed Chicago jazz cl
 ubs\, they had to adapt their music to be heard\, and they created the ico
 nic and influential style we hear today. Learn about some favorite Chicago
  blues musicians\, the history of the Chicago blues\, and how it changed t
 he music that came after.Each Music Monday event includes a presentation r
 elated to music history\, followed by discussion.
CATEGORIES:Arts and Culture,Discussion
