DESCRIPTION:Featuring Northwestern piano students nominated by the Bienen 
 School piano faculty\, this annual competition was established by the late
  violin professor Samuel Thaviu and his wife\, Elinor Thaviu\, to honor th
 e late piano professor Donald Isaak. The Thaviu/Isaak Award in Piano Perfo
