 ys playing tennis and participating in tennis summer camps.Pianist Edie Pa
 rk is a junior at the Latin School of Chicago. She studies piano with Mart
 a Aznavoorian and is a scholarship fellow of the Music Institute of Chicag
 o Academy. Edie won honorable mention in the 2024 Fox Valley Orchestra Con
 certo Competition\, first place and best interpretation of Korean music in
