DESCRIPTION:Owning a home takes a lot of time\, money\, and energy\, so it 
 important to know about the process  of purchasing a home. This webinar c
 overs what a lender looks for in a loan application\, credit basics\, down
  payments\, and the players in the home buying process. This webinar is p
 art of Financial Fitness 2026\, a free financial literacy series presented
  by BIG (Business Interest Group)\, comprised of business librarians in th
 e Chicago suburbs. These virtual programs offer practical tips and advice 
 from experienced financial advisors.Register here to receive a Zoom link.K
 eyword: Consumer Information
CATEGORIES:Self-Improvement
