SUMMARY:Financial Fitness: Retirement Reality with Jill Schlesinger [Z]
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.lincolnwoodlibrary.org/event/financial-fitness-re
 tirement-reality-jill-schlesinger-z-34976
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260225T023339Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260302T212920Z
DESCRIPTION:Presented as part of the Financial Fitness 2026 series\, this o
 nline program features CBS News Business Analyst Jill Schlesinger\, CFP\, 
 discussing practical steps toward retirement planning. The program address
 es strategies for those early in their careers as well as those preparing 
 to wind down\, helping demystify personal finances and build confidence fo
 r the future.This virtual program is part of Financial Fitness 2026\, a fr
 ee financial literacy series presented by BIG (Business Interest Group)\,a
  group of business librarians in the Chicago suburbs in support of the lib
 raries’ mission of providing access to reliable information\; these virt
 ual programs offer practical tips and advice from experienced financial ad
 visors.Register Here!
CATEGORIES:STEAM,Adult Learning
