DESCRIPTION:A reluctant but energetic America entered the fighting in 1917.
  We sent our sons. We rationed our bread. We stopped wearing corsets to sa
 ve the steel for warships… and we wrote and sang the songs that rallied 
 the troops.  Ellie from ElliePresents will transport the audience there w
 ith the sights\, sounds and tastes of the era.
