 rs form a Neil Diamond tribute band\, proving it's never too late to find 
 love and follow your dreams. Hamnet (2025)Mon\, Apr 27 • 1-3:30pm • 
 PG-13\, 125 mins • [D]William Shakespeare and his wife\, Agnes\, celebra
 te the birth of their son\, Hamnet. However\, when tragedy strikes and Ham
 net dies at a young age\, it inspires Shakespeare to write his timeless ma
 sterpiece Hamlet.
