 on College students.\n\n \n\n2026 Appointment Dates:\n\nFebruary 4March 4Ap
 ril 1May 6 \n\nAppointments are available from 12:00 - 2:00 p.m.\n\n\nPleas
 e email OAEDsupport@oakton.edu or call 847.376.7298 if you have any questio
 ns or would like to schedule an appointment. You must make an appointment. 
 Walk-ins are not accepted.\n\n\n*Please let us know up to 3 days prior to y
 our session which language you prefer.\n\n \n\nIndividuals with disabilitie
 s who would like to request an accommodation or who have questions about ac
 cessibility\, please make sure to contact us at least two weeks prior to yo
 ur appointment.
