 ng is being held at the Skokie Public Library\, in the Cosmos Room.The boo
 k can be checked out through all library ebook platforms\, including Hoopl
 a where copies are always available. Find instructions on our Download & S
 tream page\, or contact us for assistance.Book Synopsis: Struggling to ful
 fill a terminally ill father's final bequest\, a privileged Chinese-Americ
 an family in Silicon Valley is forced to contend with the realities of the
 ir ambitions and actual desires.
