UID:23847
DTSTAMP:20260313T021959Z
SUMMARY:Mystery Book Club
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.skokielibrary.info/event/mystery-book-club-case-m
 issing-maid-23847
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260203T204311Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T173200Z
DESCRIPTION:This month we'll be discussing The Case of the Missing Maid by 
 Rob Osler. As the Prescott Detective Agency’s only female operative\, H
 arriet Morrow must work with what she’s given\, an elderly\, eccentric c
 lient certain that her housekeeper has met with foul play. But discovering
  the places in Chicago where women who like women and men who like men gat
 her may force Ms. Morrow to face the parts of herself she keeps hidden. Se
 t in 1898\, this is a mystery rich in both local and queer history.  Fin
 d The Case of the Missing Maid in the library catalog.
CATEGORIES:Books and Authors,Discussion
DTSTART:20260604T000000Z
DTEND:20260604T013000Z
LOCATION:5215 Oakton Street\, Skokie\, IL\, 60077\, US
ROOM:Cosmos Room
GEO:42.0258969;-87.7580355
END:VEVENT
