STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260204T015141Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T201435Z
DESCRIPTION:Wicked: For GoodOnce more\, we are in the wonderful world of Oz
 . Wicked: For Good is the second chapter of a two-part adaptation of the 
 hit musical play. Indeed\, times are turbulent\, and all is not as it see
 ms—the Wizard lies\, propaganda spreads\, and many innocent Ozians are b
 eing suppressed. Elphaba\, rebellious as ever\, fights against injustices 
 and is branded as the Wicked Witch of the West\; meanwhile\, Glinda\, driv
 en by a need to conform and be liked\, becomes the beloved Good Witch. Wil
 l the two—once-best friends\, now public adversaries—find a way to wor
 k together and change Oz for the better?Starring Ariana Grande\, Cynthia E
 rivo\, Jonathan Bailey\, Ethan Slater\, Bowen Yang\, Marissa Bode\, Colman
  Domingo\, Michelle Yeoh\, and Jeff Goldblum. Directed by Jon M. Chu.2025 
 : 137 minutes : Rated PG-13 for action/violence\, some suggestive material
 \, and thematic material : MusicalFree tickets will be given to those who 
 attend. Watch a trailer for Wicked: For Good.Find Wicked: For Good in the
  library catalog.
CATEGORIES:Movie
